\fs32 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\cf2 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Large\uc0\u8209 scale AI catalogs are allowed only if each ebook stands on its own merit: original text, clear structure, accurate metadata, and no policy\u8209 violating content (e.g., explicit, harmful, or fraudulent material).\
\ls9\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\cf2 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Upload volume itself is not the violation; it is mass uploading of repetitive, misleading, or low\uc0\u8209 quality AI books that triggers enforcement under spam and content\u8209 quality rules.\
